             sworn.</p>
               <p>I heard the prisoner running; he ran through the White-lion, in Fashion-street; at the back door I overtook him, and in the left side of his coat, I found this milk pot.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
               <p>Mrs. ALEXANDER sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner in the room, putting his hand on the milk pot, and I cried out my milk pot, stop thief; he ran out, and I after him.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I and my mother had been selling chip hats; I came into this house, and had a pint of beer; and the gentleman persuaded this gentlewoman to swear that I took it; I have been almost four months in confinement.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17860830-66-verdict340" type="verdictDescription">
